name: Carte.js
body:
# carte.js
WebGL Visualization for Google Maps


# Fast
Renders points, polygons and rasters multiple times faster than canvas.
Minimal draw calls by using texture atlases generated on the fly to render objects by batch.

# Supports tiling
Automatically renders tiles from either vector or image sources.
Currently supports sources from /z/x/y tile servers with either GeoJSON or PNG formats.
Caches each tile so dragging and panning is smooth once all tiles are loaded.

# Extendable
Will be adding more file formats possibly including MVT, TopoJSON and other custom binary formats.
